e program was born.\r\n\r\nSince it’s conception, Alley Art Amazin’ has grown to include more than 50 murals and art pieces scattered about Old Town’s alleyways. As we are entering our fifth season, Alley Art Amazin’ art directors are gearing up to bring their talent and paint brushes to help residents and business paint new ‘canvases’.\r\n\r\nOur goal is to engage the community to tap into their inner creativity, working with professional artists to give life and art to Lafayette’s alleyways and side streets. We aim to continue to give Old Town Lafayette colorful and inviting galleries of public art, just a walk or bike ride away . We also promote the curbing of unwanted tagging and graffiti. By beautifying the alleyways, sheds, outbuildings and fences of Old Town Lafayette, the Alley Art Amazin’ program inspires creativity, encourages exploration and bonds our unique community." margin_bottom="marg-bottom-30" text_align="text-center" tag="h2" tag_marg_bottom="default"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row progress_img="no" box_padding="pad-40" theme_color="theme-color" transparent_bg="transparent-bg-0" parallax="" bgtype="image" bgfixed="no"][vc_column width="1/2"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id="post-widget"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row box_padding="pad-top-bottom-80" theme_color="darkness" transparent_bg="transparent-bg-0" progress_img="no" bgtype="image" bgfixed="no" css=".vc_custom_1430944115470{background-image: url(http://grenadelounge.com/AlleyArt-2/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Old_Town_Lafayette_24.jpg?id=4551) !important;}" parallax="yes" extra_css="pattern"][vc_column width="1/1" text_align="text-center" css_animation_type="fadeInUp"][vc_add_heading title="Old Town Lafayette Artwork" text_align="text-center" border_bottom="yes" css_animation_type="fadeInUp" margin_bottom="marg-bottom-30" tag="h2" tag_marg_bottom="default"][vc_portfolio_grid type="4colwithouttext" num="8" filter="yes" view_more="no"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css="